name: Digital Delay DD600
details:
Digital Stereo Delay/EchoThe feature-packed DD600 is the ultimate digital effects pedal – for everything from short and subtle, to show-stopping 2-second delays (echo). Compare the DD600 to state-of-the-art, studio-grade processors costing 3 times as much – and you’ll find yourself coming to the DD600 pedal every time. Our amazing RSM technology and high-resolution 24-bit processing will keep you sounding your best, time after time, after time.
